  Locus:
    Page: 137
    Verse: 13
Tags:
  - Evil
---
Every evil thought or deed or hatred, or any other thought or reaction if
it is controlled, will be laid in our favor. It is not that we lose by thus
restraining ourselves; we are gaining infinitely more than we suspect.
